{"tid":2295514,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"廿零歲 法國自己已經被磨折得好痛苦","createTime":"2020-11-22T00:19:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T13:42:58.000Z","uid":378342,"like":7,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"9ad01359fffd69a3d4a85a6ef8c293182d2536a0","tid":2295514,"uid":378342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T00:19:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中學畢業之後 就開始做埋d垃圾飲食工 勞動工<br />\n然後日校 夜校 考牌<br />\n基本上無停過返工<br />\n其實錢又唔係真係好缺 但唔敢停 一停就好似會跑輸咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係好攰了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />作為一條女 返份工要返六日 一日做十幾個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />開始老得好快<br />\n但始終都係揾得唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我只係想證明到自己有用<br />\n點解咁難<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能我資質差 唔配得到賞識<br />\n<br />\n已經對所有野都失去左興趣 個人變到好麻木冷血<br />\n對人無哂感情 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我屌<br />\n有人追都唔想拍拖 因為覺得佢地好廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我就黎發癲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚寂莫啊<br />\n陪我傾下計好嗎"},{"pid":"99785864f0cebc40b652228b2d6a41e98d903736","tid":2295514,"uid":104804,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T00:27:02.000Z","msg":"做it support啦<br />\nhea下又一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2221b9974a2a5b4f87c90931381c3f6ffd0360ae","tid":2295514,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T00:29:35.000Z","msg":"係時候要休息<br />\n抖下<br />\nBye bye<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"069644ad5fb3b4e272e9d1c15dab32566f41f4a7","tid":2295514,"uid":116827,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T00:36:49.000Z","msg":"做人做到無夢想<br />\n不如包養更輕鬆"},{"pid":"9bb127